brother-label-printer (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added "Text Only" tab for printing text-only labels without QR codes
  * Text is centered both horizontally and vertically on labels
  * Reorganized tabs: "QR + Text", "Batch Mode", and "Text Only"
  * Added create_text_only_label() function for centered text labels

 -- Daniel Rosehill <public@danielrosehill.com>  Fri, 20 Dec 2024 18:15:00 +0200

brother-label-printer (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Single label printing with QR codes
  * Batch mode for up to 10 labels
  * Support for multiple tape widths (29mm, 38mm, 50mm, 62mm)
  * Preview functionality
  * Keyboard shortcuts
  * Customizable fonts and sizes

